Subject: [PATCH 2/4] lsws: add NV15 and NV20 formats support

Signed-off-by: nyanmisaka <nst799610810@gmail.com>
(cherry picked from commit e15477c0199a5e870e5e76287f46472a649b4faa)
---
 libswscale/format.c           |  2 +
 libswscale/input.c            | 41 +++++++++++++++++++++
 libswscale/swscale_unscaled.c | 69 +++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
 tests/ref/fate/imgutils       |  4 ++
 4 files changed, 116 insertions(+)

diff --git a/libswscale/format.c b/libswscale/format.c
